snippet.title: Up-Cycled BT Workshop Trailer Build: Finishing Touches - Finale
snippet.description:
Blinkist 25% off here: http://www.blinkist.com/projectamber

This is the last in the series of the up-cycled trailer build. I attach a new hitch and finish the last of the jobs on my to do list before relocating it and us down south for the next big project.


Subscribe to keep up with Project.Amber:
https://www.youtube.com/c/projectamber
